{"sectionId":776,"sectionIdLiteral":"776","humanId":"lesson-351","volumeId":"workbook","locale":"en","titleInfo":{"title":"My sinless brother is my guide to peace.  My sinful brother is my guide to pain.  And which I choose to see I will behold.","ownlineNumber":"Lesson 351"},"annotation":"W-351","bodyHtml":"<div class=\"acim-text lesson-351\"> <div data-paragraph-id=\"776#1\"><p class=\"p-italic\"><span class=\"pnr\">1.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"776#1:1\"><span class=\"snr noprint\">1</span>Who is my brother but Your holy Son?</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"776#1:2\"><span class=\"snr\">2</span>And if I see him sinful I proclaim myself a sinner, not a Son of God; alone and friendless in a fearful world.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"776#1:3\"><span class=\"snr\">3</span>Yet this perception is a choice I make, and can relinquish.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"776#1:4\"><span class=\"snr\">4</span>I can also see my brother sinless, as Your holy Son.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"776#1:5\"><span class=\"snr\">5</span>And with this choice I see my sinlessness, my everlasting Comforter and Friend beside me, and my way secure and clear.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"776#1:6\"><span class=\"snr\">6</span>Choose, then, for me, my Father, through Your Voice.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"776#1:7\"><span class=\"snr\">7</span>For He alone gives judgment in Your Name.</span></p></div> </div>","firstWords":"Who is my brother but Your holy Son? And if I see him sinful I proclaim myself a sinner, not a Son of God; alone and friendless in a fearful world. Yet this perception is a choice I make, and can","contentType":"acim-content","seoTitle":"Lesson 351: My sinless brother is my guide to‚Ä¶ | ACIM","seoDescription":"‚ú® A Course in Miracles with üéß Audio! Read and listen to Lesson¬†351 ‚ÄúMy sinless brother is my guide to peace. My sinful brother is my guide to pain. And which I choose to see I will behold‚Äù: ‚Ä¶","desktopBreadcrumbs":[{"label":"Workbook","le